sub_title: EMBA Project Manager and Business Analyst
summary:
I am committed making the environment in which I work a productive, efficient and pleasant place.
My nature, my passions, the continuous desire to travel connected to a good dose of curiosity and the work path taken so far have made me a positive, enthusiastic and organized person.
I am sensitive to issues such as ethics, sustainability, autonomy and clarity.

Among the technical and process skills I feel I can say about myself:
project management, costing and costing product, process organization, resource management, proposal formulation and purchasing process.

While among the transversal ones:
ability to diagnose, flexible, concise, decision making.

I speak Italian as native language, English (C2) and a little French (B1).

IT skills: Microsoft Office, SAP (as User MM), Miles

Digital Skills: Autonomous / Advanced
